    public abstract class KeyRelationshipInformation
extends RelationshipInformation
    Handles the metadata for the ReflectiveNeo4JNodeRepositoryImpl It contains information on a Map relationship Map<Key, NODE> where the Key will be moved into a MapRelationship.
